```cs
using System;

public struct Foo : IDisposable
{
    public int a;
    
    public void Dispose()
    {
        a++;
    }
}

class Program
{
    static void Main()
    {
        var foo = new Foo();
        
        using (var bar = foo)
        {
            using (var baz = bar)
            {
                Console.Write(baz.a);
            }
            Console.Write(bar.a);
        }
        Console.Write(foo.a);
    }
}
```
